,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T20:05:27.000Z","msg":"因為要用歌詞叫春"},{"pid":"d30d2cbaf74f5bc4f4da3aa7a2dfffc845579299","tid":909263,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"8a8e5a50d75892d7cebe4e89b63336843244f2c1","tid":909263,"uid":214036,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"fa273c809a5d136e529e89d66e762a407d4732b0","tid":909263,"uid":31215,"like":7,"dislike":8,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T12:41:41.000Z","msg":"好曲<br />\n只會令人覺得好聽<br />\n<br />\n好詞<br />\n先會令人有強烈共鳴同啟發<br />\n唔同意嘅人<br />\n你搵首純音樂表達下任我行意見我睇？<br />\n通常純音樂曲要有追加意思，要理解首曲表後時代同作者心境，咪又係要字附助解釋<br />\n<br />\n而好詞<br />\n要留白先可以雋永，有深度<br />\n所以苦瓜同任我行<br />\n意境上同啟發性係任我行高啲<br />\n中華文化，要含蓄，看穿不說穿，要自己領會先係上品<br />\n<br />\n所以廢詞，最多都只能達到好聽<br />\n直白好詞，只能達到有意思<br />\n含蓄好詞，上品"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T18:57:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T02:04:04.000Z","msg":"曲只可以渲染到大概嘅情緒<br />\n細節野同具體野表達不能<br />\n啲曲撚好鍾意加一句唔同人聽，唔同時間聽有唔同感受<br />\n但如果唔追求自己ff，要準確啲了解歌想表達嘅野，而唔係用完自己角度去理解，都係要去返字<br />\n<br />\n一首輕快嘅歌，最多只會覺得係渲染快樂<br />\n但邊種快樂，打贏仗開心？推翻暴政開心？豐收開心？有喜事開心？<br />\n一首sweet melody<br />\n係同男朋友開心？曖昧開心？偷食成功開心？暗戀開心？<br />\n<br />\n已經估唔撚到<br />\n<br />\n淨係嗰年新年歌，選用樂器，旋律嗰啲咁特色，一聽就知新年到但冇字點知邊首講發財，邊首講家人團聚，邊首講一年之初的喜悅？"},{"pid":"bde7ea2aae3656d16197492fd6c152fa99bbea4a","tid":909263,"uid":184592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T02:21:14.000Z","msg":"<strong>Bruno Mars - When I Was Your Man</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ekzHIouo8Q4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FekzHIouo8Q4&d=Q2fpNZjU8e7BPMXOjrwcQROFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=ca213727\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ekzHIouo8Q4</a><br />\nSame bed but it feels just a little bit bigger now<br />\nOur song on the radio but it don't sound the same<br />\nWhen our friends talk about you, all it does is just tear me down<br />\n'Cause my heart breaks a little when I hear your name<br />\nIt all just sounds like ooh, ooh ooh hoo hoo<br />\nMm, too young, too dumb to realize<br />\nThat I should have bought you flowers<br />\nAnd held your hand<br />\nShould have gave you all my hours<br />\nWhen I had the chance<br />\nTake you to every party 'cause all you wanted to do was dance<br />\nNow my baby's dancing<br />\nBut she's dancing with another man"},{"pid":"936a75e924f2f5a385925a803cc74f3f968aab7f","tid":909263,"uid":184592,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T02:23:48.000Z","msg":"係咪廣東詞難填，一填得差就好覺眼？<br />\n美式詞例如 Bruno Mars 首When I was your man，小學生level，但唱出真感情<br />\n英式詞例如 Suede嘅The 2 of Us 好似寫詩咁<br />\n<br />\n利伸：聽曲多"},{"pid":"13b84e339783f3aec82953b528c81e149995548f","tid":909263,"uid":185038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T02:23:59.000Z","msg":"其實大部份廣東歌歌詞比起其他語言既歌詞有深度好多 利申乜春都聽"},{"pid":"e35a5edb99dfdeb4fb7211d2ce482f4089772d16","tid":909263,"uid":184592,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"17bdfa6e1aa3d8ba98190b4b08f438d6cddef37f","tid":909263,"uid":209432,"like":6,"dislike":32,"score":-26,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T10:17:28.000Z","msg":"如果用歌黎喻人<br />\n曲係一首歌既外在；<br />\n詞就係歌既內涵底蘊。<br />\n比起旋律入面既情感，歌詞先至係真真正正首歌想表達既訊息，如果曲夠好但詞填得差係糟蹋咗首歌，廣東歌特別難填大家都知，用英文同普通話要填啲不過不失既詞係相對簡單好多，而且廣東話讀起上黎有種天然既口語感，填得太直白讀起上黎的確係比較奇怪。"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T02:26:28.000Z","msg":"//比起旋律入面既情感，歌詞先至係真真正正首歌想表達既訊息//<br />\n古典音樂無詞添，一樣表達到訊息"},{"pid":"c520398beb774d7584e797868442a8e932096b4c","tid":909263,"uid":184592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"441d45c9f8ba08849136b765436a732b6f91eb75","tid":909263,"uid":13067,"like":1,"dislike":13,"score":-12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T08:46:58.000Z","msg":"詞的確係重要過曲WO"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T02:33:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/liTSRH4fix4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FliTSRH4fix4&d=Q2fpNZjU8e7BPMXOjrwcQROFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=cea93774\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/li